text: Hana Kafková (born 26 June 1965) is a Czech rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
